  "prompt": "What are some toy manufacturers in Mexico?",
  "response": "Mexico has a vibrant toy manufacturing industry, with several companies involved in the production of toys and games. Here are some notable toy manufacturers based in Mexico:\n\n1. **Grupo Juguetes Mosaico** - Specializes in a variety of toys, including educational and action toys.\n  \n2. **F\u00e1brica de Juguetes El \u00c1guila** - A well-known manufacturer producing various types of toys, focusing on quality and safety.\n\n3. **Juguetes Pineda Covalin** - Known for traditional and cultural-themed toys that reflect Mexican heritage.\n\n4. **Juguetes Juguet\u00f3n** - Manufactures different types of toys, including plush toys and novelties.\n\n5. **Bromas de M\u00e9xico** - Specializes in novelty toys and prank items.\n\n6. **Juguetes Roma** - Produces a range of toys, catering to different age groups and interests.\n\nIn addition to these manufacturers, many international toy companies have factories or sourcing operations in Mexico due to the country\u2019s proximity to the U.S. market and its skilled labor force. This includes companies like Mattel and Hasbro, which may utilize Mexican facilities for their production needs.",
